data.description:
Welcome to your new home oasis within city limits. This exquisite ranch-style home, priced at $319,000 is designed for those who appreciate both comfort and sophistication.
Step into a world of spaciousness and functionality, ideal for both comfortable living and entertaining. The versatile basement space adds an extra layer of luxury, perfect for additional living quarters or your favorite recreational activities.
The upgraded features, including stunning hardwood floors, showcase the attention to detail throughout the entire home. Your convenience is taken care of with a secure 2-car garage, ensuring both parking and storage are hassle-free.
Escape to your serene outdoor space surrounded by nature, creating a peaceful retreat right at your doorstep. Enjoy the tranquility of the location while still being close to major highways and quality schools, enhancing your daily lifestyle.
This remarkable ranch-style home boasts two non-conforming bedrooms in the basement, providing flexibility for your unique needs. And here's the exciting news – the seller is thrilled to offer a $5,000 contribution towards your closing costs, making this opportunity even more irresistible!
Discover the joys of residing in the Raytown School district, with the Heart of America Golf course just a stone's throw away. Embrace the outdoors with easy access to Longview Lake beach, Kauffman memorial garden park, and the tomahawk creek hiking trail.
For those with an active lifestyle, the nearest gym is a mere 0.9 miles away, ensuring fitness is always within reach. And when it's time to unwind, a movie theater awaits just 4.4 miles away.
Don't let this incredible opportunity slip through your fingers! Contact me today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm and convenience of this spectacular home. Your dream home journey begins here.
